{"type":"text","timestamp":1775896168786,"sessionID":"ses_284590c14ffe8XlWT84CyDeEpH","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba8d7d5001II1h700HmPVOrK","messageID":"msg_d7ba8c5dc001hj96NbsvwARRHP","sessionID":"ses_284590c14ffe8XlWT84CyDeEpH","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-024 archive documents, here is the summary:\n\n---\n\n## AR-024 — DockerService 封装 Archive Summary\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n**Core Implementation (agentcube/services/docker_service.py):**\n- `DockerService` class with lazy-initialized Docker client\n- `_get_client()` with health check via `ping()`\n- `is_docker_available()` for Docker daemon status checking\n- `_format_image_id()` helper (12-character truncation)\n\n**Image Operations:**\n- `build_image()` — Full implementation with Dockerfile validation, build args support, error extraction from build logs, build time tracking, and size formatting\n- `tag_image()` — Tag existing images with source/target handling\n- `get_image_info()` — Retrieve image details (size, created, labels)\n- `list_images()` — List all images with optional name filtering\n\n**Registry Operations:**\n- `push_image()` — Push to Docker Hub or custom registry with authentication support\n- `extract_credentials_from_url()` — Parse `user:pass@host` format with URL decoding\n\n**Package Integration:**\n- `DockerService` exported from `agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n\n**Documentation:**\n- Module and class docstrings\n- Type hints on all methods\n- Comprehensive proposal.md with verification examples\n\n---\n\n### ⏸️ Deferred\n\n**Per proposal.md Out of Scope:**\n1. **Docker Compose** — Multi-container orchestration\n2. **Volume Management** — Docker volume creation/management\n3. **Network Management** — Docker network configuration\n4. **Container Runtime** — Running and managing containers (only image operations implemented)\n5. **Registry Management** — Creating/managing registry repositories\n6. **Image Scanning** — Security scanning\n7. **Multi-platform Builds** — Cross-platform image builds\n8. **BuildKit Features** — Advanced BuildKit syntax\n\n**From Original spec.yaml Scope:**\n- Container lifecycle operations (create, start, stop, remove)\n- Network operations (create, list, remove)\n- Volume management (create, list, remove)\n\n**Testing (from tasks.md):**\n- All unit tests (ST-4.8 through ST-4.12) — 34 test tasks deferred\n- Integration tests (ST-4.13) — 7 test tasks deferred\n- No test files exist in the repository\n\n**Additional Deferred from Design:**\n- Docker Exceptions module (`docker_exceptions.py`)\n- Docker Configuration module (`docker_config.py`)\n- Dual backend strategy (CLI fallback not implemented — SDK only)\n\n---\n\n### Status\n- **Implementation:** ~65% complete (image operations done, container/volume/network deferred)\n- **Tests:** 0% (all deferred)\n- **Documentation:** 80% (code documented, tests not)","time":{"start":1775896168783,"end":1775896168783}}}
